name: tezos_blockchain_24_09_2021
description:
This is a generative art piece created from all of the transactions completed on September 24th 2021 (using the GMT timezone) on the Tezos mainnet.

The style is "Blockchain". Each pixel that is not the background color, #000000 in this piece, represents a unique address that participated in these transactions. The pixels are colored used a heatmap approach where addresses that participated in more transactions have a brighter, more vibrant color. The pixels are then ordered to illustrate a chain of blocks.
